elf\n| Episode: \"Joel McHale Wears a Navy Zip-up and High Tops\"\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[BoJack Horseman]]''\n| Alex (voice)\n| Episode: \"Yesterdayland\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132018\n| ''{{sortname|The|X-Files}}''\n| Tad O'Malley\n| 4 episodes \n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Dr. Ken]]''\n| Ross\n| Episode: \"Dave's Valentine\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Difficult People]]''\n| Felix\n| Episode: \"Hashtag Cats\"\n|-\n| 2016 \n| ''[[Lip Sync Battle]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"[[Jim Rash]] vs. Joel McHale\"\n|-\n| 2016\u20132017\n| ''{{sortname|The|Great Indoors|dab=TV series}}''\n| Jack Gordon\n| 22 episodes\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Dimension 404]]''\n| Dr. Matthew Maker\n| Episode: \"Matchmaker\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Mystery Science Theater 3000]]''\n| [[Doug McClure]]\n| Episode: \"At the Earth's Core\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Rick and Morty]]''\n| Death Stalker Hemorrhage (voice)\n| Episode: \"Rickmancing the Stone\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Milo Murphy's Law]]''\n| Victor Verliezer (voice)\n| Episode: \"A Clockwork Origin\"\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[Ryan Hansen Solves Crimes on Television]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Joel HcHale Is: Ryan Hansen\"\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[The Joel McHale Show with Joel McHale]]''\n| Himself (host)\n| 19 episodes; also writer and executive producer\n|-\n| 2018\u20132019\n| ''[[Santa Clarita Diet]]''\n| Chris\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Drunk History]]''\n| [[George Corwin]], [[Robert Ellis Cahill]]\n| Episode: \"Halloween\"\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Masked Singer (American TV series)|The Masked Singer]]''\n| Himself\n| 3 episodes\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[RuPaul's Drag Race]]''\n| Himself (guest judge)\n| Season 11, episode 4\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Rookie (TV series)|The Rookie]]''\n| Brad Hayes<ref>{{cite episode |title=The Shake Up |series=The Rookie |network=[[American Broadcasting Company|ABC]] |date=March 26, 2019 |season=1 |number=17}}</ref>\n| Episode: \"The Shake Up\"\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Card Sharks]]''\n| Host and executive producer\n| 5 episodes\n|-\n| 2019\n|''[[Mr. Iglesias]]''\n| Danny\n| Episode: \"Oh Boy, Danny\"\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[What Just Happened??! with Fred Savage]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Preetempted\"\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Stargirl (TV series)|Stargirl]]''\n| [[Sylvester Pemberton|Sylvester Pemberton / Starman]]\n| Recurring role\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[The Twilight Zone (2019 TV series)|The Twilight Zone]]''\n| TBA\n| Episode: \"8\"\n|-\n| 2020\n| ''[[Tiger King]]''\n| Himself (host)\n| Episode: \"The Tiger King and I\"\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Lego Dimensions]]''\n| X-PO\n|-\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Work\n! Result\n|-\n| 2010\n| [[EWwy Award]]\n| Best Actor in a Comedy\n| rowspan=\"10\" | ''[[Community (TV series)|Community]]''\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2011\n| [[1st Critics' Choice Television Awards|Critics' Choice Television Award]]\n| [[Critics' Choice Television Award for Best Actor in a Comedy Series|Best Actor in a Comedy Series]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| EWwy Award\n| Best Actor in a Comedy\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[16th Satellite Awards|Satellite Award]]\n| [[Satellite Award for Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Musical or Comedy|Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Musical or Comedy]]\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"6\" | 2012\n| [[TV Guide Award]]\n| Favorite Ensemble\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[2nd Critics' Choice Television Awards|Critics' Choice Television Award]]\n| Best Actor in a Comedy Series\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |[[Pan-American Association of Film & Television Journalists|PAAFTJ Television Award]]\n| Best Lead Actor in a Comedy Series\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Best Cast in a Comedy Series\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| EWwy Award\n| Best Actor, Comedy\n| {{won}}\n|-\n| [[17th Satellite Awards|Satellite Award]]\n| Best Actor \u2013 Television Series Musical or Comedy\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2014\n| [[66th Primetime Emmy Awards|Primetime Emmy Award]]\n| Outstanding Short-Format Live-Action